              acceptedAnswers: ["-1", "T", "T,"],
              explanation: "positions.view(1, 1, T, 1) shapes the position indices as (batch=1, head=1, seq=T, dim=1). Broadcasting then multiplies each of the T positions by each of the N frequencies."
