              acceptedAnswers: ["x @ W_enc", "torch.matmul(x, W_enc)"],
              explanation: "x @ W_enc performs the expansion from token space (D) to sparse latent space (nh*N). Each token's D-dimensional representation is projected into a much wider space where k-WTA competition happens."
